{"id":"3d0e1ec53377c784ea0a0e50455866f80d589f102344113a1262238e8138e7ef","item_id":"3ac31554be:0","text":"下面示例展示如何将 Ri Attributes（例如 Ri Round Curve）导出到 Alembic File，以便读入 RenderMan for Maya（RfM）；RfM 期望使用 rman__，而不是 Houdini 历来使用的 ri_。"}
{"id":"d6ce50883336ba4f9197db6ab666e7d93b430d362dd56ecf97c0f99652a30c73","item_id":"3ac31554be:1","text":"添加一个"}
{"id":"fef86e8ff28d2acff271b84cc42a8300748108de36879a8120655a6c01c27659","item_id":"3ac31554be:2","text":"AttributeCreate"}
{"id":"2e845edd8b19f4bdac6cb24a0be5539eb8436d3a2fe4dbf0d234a09a9d04627a","item_id":"3ac31554be:3","text":"节点。"}
{"id":"41808c26c28a3f4df348e8e80784f8d6642e4ea539f4086c8b2af5fd808e7b67","item_id":"3ac31554be:4","text":"将 Name（名称）设置为 RenderMan for Maya 中使用的命名方式，例如 rman__riattr__dice_roundcurve"}
{"id":"6eb744f546ee91168d1d690ab0fd212e29de49662f2c422005235b956305e425","item_id":"3ac31554be:5","text":"将 Class 设置为"}
{"id":"d7747a10eddbd92c14d863e92f239c29ab5ed8dfec7566f6f5c4ac40f4981e12","item_id":"3ac31554be:6","text":"Detail"}
{"id":"a3bd5d3381c77fb7d1d6532da05cce5dc24e0176f9a47880cde39fb7bc1b884e","item_id":"3ac31554be:7","text":"将 Value 表达式设置为 Ri Attribute（例如 ri_roundcurve）"}
{"id":"53150617b1a6a723ac314a983849fd2f7243c565a662bb4899d5cba959f97a22","item_id":"3ac31554be:8","text":"可以在此处下载此示例："}
{"id":"365cc39e52d5af058fc86f9b7294b8b15303d64fa826cd454d4e6c2bf0ee3cd0","item_id":"3ac31554be:9","text":"curves_alembicattr.hip"}
{"id":"1442619f2e066179e61dc4470837c6058ca2f1d58f5793651ce8a19cfe3cda18","item_id":"3ac31554be:10","text":"将 Alembic 文件读入 RfM 后，你会看到 Round Curve 属性及其来自 Houdini 的设置。"}
